"title": "9165: restoration",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "9165",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The returning of something or someone to their original state. Through the redeeming work of Jesus Christ, both humanity and creation will eventually be restored.</p>\n<h2>Restoration of human beings through the ministry of Jesus Christ</h2>\n<h3>Restoration of health</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:38-Luke4:39\">LUK 4:38–4:39</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:43-Luke8:44\">LUK 8:43–8:44</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke14:2-Luke14:4\">LUK 14:2–14:4</a></p>\n<h3>Restoration of life</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke7:11-Luke7:15\">LUK 7:11–7:15</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John11:1-John11:44\">JHN 11:1–11:44</a></p>\n<h3>Restoration of sight</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark8:22-Mark8:25\">MRK 8:22–8:25</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John9:1-John9:7\">JHN 9:1–9:7</a></p>\n<h3>Restoration of hearing</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark7:32-Mark7:35\">MRK 7:32–7:35</a></p>\n<h2>The restoration of creation</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts3:21\">ACT 3:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa11:6-Isa11:9\">ISA 11:6–11:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa41:17-Isa41:20\">ISA 41:17–41:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa55:10-Isa55:13\">ISA 55:10–55:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:1-Rev21:4\">REV 21:1–21:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev22:1-Rev22:5\">REV 22:1–22:5</a></p>\n<h2>The restoration of Israel</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps14:7\">PSA 14:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps69:35-Ps69:36\">PSA 69:35–69:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa41:13\">ISA 41:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa51:1-Isa51:6\">ISA 51:1–51:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer30:18-Jer30:22\">JER 30:18–30:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek36:8-Ezek36:12\">EZK 36:8–36:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos9:13-Amos9:15\">AMO 9:13–9:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom11:25-Rom11:27\">ROM 11:25–11:27</a></p>\n<h2>Restoration in everyday life</h2>\n<h3>The restoration of status</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen40:13\">GEN 40:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job8:6\">JOB 8:6</a></p>\n<h3>The restoration of fortunes</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut30:3\">DEU 30:3</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek16:53\">EZK 16:53</a></p>\n<h3>The restoration of buildings</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr24:4\">2CH 24:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra5:9\">EZR 5:9</a></p>\n<h3>The restoration of authority</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam8:3\">2SA 8:3</a></p>",
